{"tid":2112823,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n間好食嘅撻","createTime":"2020-07-17T15:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T17:00:07.000Z","uid":149563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9c59bda60633f7b8c2c28476f2f78ffa227445","tid":2112823,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"最近鍾意咗食撻 <br />\n亦都想睇下有咩小店啱食<br />\n如果大家最近都有食開邊間好食不如交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時係我心目中第一位就係...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igvh6P2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Figvh6P2.png&h=881fa4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢最出名係一抹 但係自己唔係太鍾意抹茶所以一路都冇試<br />\n基本上喺門口已經聞到好香撻皮味<br />\n暫時最鍾意食就係黑武士 即係香橙朱古力<br />\n佢最驚喜嘅係入邊嗰個啫喱<br />\n而佢嘅朱古力亦都做得幾出色 係好好食嗰隻朱古力<br />\n睇得出佢每一隻撻都花心思諗材料 因為就算芝麻撻佢都會加麻糬係中間 唔會剩係得芝麻咁悶<br />\n已經回購第三次 因為真係好好食<br />\n利申 打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後係我覺得OK啦嘅舖頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Rc04Et.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Rc04Et.png&h=dd8d95ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見佢整得幾靚仔 所以都試咗<br />\n吉士系列我覺得OK啦 中規中矩<br />\n比較鍾意佢奶蓋嗰個系列 個奶蓋同啲生果都幾夾<br />\n撻皮都唔錯嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWG1O7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWG1O7g.png&h=7ceaf61f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見呢間都幾出名所以又試下<br />\n之前就試咗鐵觀音朱古力 又真係幾重鐵觀音味喎<br />\n佢個撻比我想像中大 食完之後有啲膩<br />\n其實都OK嘅 都係平均以上嘅好食<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有其他好食嘅不妨推薦下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a82f30309323ec120df621b3ac072ba5b7d0a89","tid":2112823,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xH02yA0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxH02yA0.png&h=34cc7dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順帶一提<br />\n呢間一路都好想試下 但係仲未有機會食到 <br />\n有冇人試過呢間？"},{"pid":"9cf1227f7d483b03b90288f1a48b057f8e0e7ba6","tid":2112823,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/100b0u000000jfmfq1239_Z_640_10000.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdimg04.c-ctrip.com%2Fimages%2F100b0u000000jfmfq1239_Z_640_10000.gif&h=42d7186a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"535fe77ce731016117ef20b8a2545633dd0d92d3","tid":2112823,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89965fcfbd149937ae10ba8cb2379ee94a461fc8","tid":2112823,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf1227f7d483b03b90288f1a48b057f8e0e7ba6","tid":2112823,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/100b0u000000jfmfq1239_Z_640_10000.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdimg04.c-ctrip.com%2Fimages%2F100b0u000000jfmfq1239_Z_640_10000.gif&h=42d7186a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3719e688c1e95815a95126dae2966247454187fd","tid":2112823,"uid":200402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"我條女個撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1c900a6d3853f79e8e4f7b763dcc36121b659d","tid":2112823,"uid":299794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"Crazypie唔好食..."},{"pid":"58de8750dc9dbf176b2e5904858c318ccf1da3e9","tid":2112823,"uid":340796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"Tartes &amp; Pop<br />\n上環<